pxSQLStatementPost: SELECT "PC0"."name" AS "Name" , "Email"."pzinskey" AS "pzInsKey" , COUNT("PC0"."name") AS "pySummaryCount(1)" FROM pegadata.pr_Index_Data_NLP_Topic "PC0" LEFT OUTER JOIN pegadata.pc_work "Email" ON ( ( "PC0"."pxinsindexedkey" = "Email"."pzinskey" )  AND "Email"."pxobjclass" = ?  AND "PC0"."pxobjclass" = ? ) WHERE  ( "PC0"."name" IN (? , ? , ? , ? ) )  AND "PC0"."pxobjclass" = ?  GROUP BY "PC0"."name" , "Email"."pzinskey" ORDER BY 1 ASC, 2 ASC
